data.description: Make your appointment to see this beautiful move in ready brick home in Spring Ridge Subdivision today! 4 BR 2 BA, open floor plan, situated on a cul-de-sac. The main living area has wood floors and the great room has a cathedral ceiling and wood burning fire place. Split bedroom plan, large updated kitchen with granite and stainless steel appliances and breakfast area. HVAC is only 5 years old, roof only 8 years old. Home has a large patio and a private fenced back yard with a shed for your tools and toys. This home is just minutes away from Fort Moore, downtown dining and entertainment, and shopping.
